# make-README

To use this makefile on your system:

1. Modify/create make-compiler-xxx to reflect your compiler environment.

2. Modify/create make-0-xxx to reflect what you want to compile

3. Modify makefile to include make-0-xxx of step 2.

4. <Optional> To create dependencies (do this after you have moved or added files):  
   make depend 
   - This requires some form of /bin/perl. See top line of file make-depend-perl.
   - Outputs dependencies to file make-depend-output.

5. To compile your code:
   make 

6. To clean up the directory: 
   make clean 
